Class PatternPomAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PomAnalyzer

    public class PatternPomAnalyzer
extends AbstractPomAnalyzer
    PomAnalyzer implementation which uses a set of regular expressions to validate that the topmost reactor and parent POMs are valid.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
